column5: We got out this morning. Did the ice check  We are the  GOOD OLE BYES
Nice vid, thanks, I'm sure the others will appreciate it.

Just a question bud.  My bro and i are in a tournament in february on kemp and was wondering what would you use for bait to catch pike?  Biggest fish wins so i dont even want any perch even if its 15 inches. Planning on using a swedish pimple with a minnow head attached to it.
it was fun here is my take on it

I fished the first one. 8" perch won me a chain saw. Pike, yer going to have to have a Horse Shoe. Perch,white fish, herring and lakers. Even smelt, and they won a prize as well. Dont over think. Im on the fence to fish it this year.  We always have a good time buddy. Thanks for hanging
I see Santa forgot to bring the razors again...
Thanks for the look see and for posting. Cheers, Mark
Thanks for the advice.  Good luck if you enter.
